---
tags: [ screenshot, annotation, wayland ]
---
# General
Enter               Save to clipboard & exit
Esc                 Exit without saving
Ctrl+z              Undo
Ctrl+y              Redo
Ctrl+s              Save to file
Ctrl+Shift+s        Save with dialog
Ctrl+c              Copy to clipboard
Ctrl+t              Toggle toolbars
Delete              Clear all annotations
Alt+Arrows          Pan image

# Tool selection
p                   Pointer (select/move)
b                   Brush (freehand)
r                   Rectangle
e                   Ellipse
z                   Arrow
i                   Line
t                   Text
m                   Numbered marker
u                   Blur
g                   Highlight
c                   Crop

# Colors
1-9, 0              Select color from palette

# Tool modifiers
Shift               Snap angles (15°) for arrow/line
Alt                 Center origin for rectangle/ellipse
Shift               Square/circle constraint

# Text tool
Shift+Enter         Insert line break
Ctrl+Left/Right     Word jump
Ctrl+Backspace      Delete word
Enter/Esc           Accept/discard text
Ctrl+a              Select all
Ctrl+Shift+c        Copy selection
Ctrl+x              Cut
Ctrl+v              Paste

# Hyprland keybindings
Print               Screenshot area → clipboard
Shift+Print         Full screenshot → clipboard
Ctrl+Print          Window screenshot → clipboard
Alt+Print           Screenshot area → Satty
Super+Shift+Print   Full screenshot → Satty
Super+Ctrl+Print    Window screenshot → Satty
Super+Alt+Print     Open clipboard in Satty
